| A05 Security Misconfiguration | Missing `helmet`, `x-powered-by` still set — **real finding** |
| A06 Vulnerable Components | Can't assess without `package.json`/lockfile — run `npm audit` |
| A07 Auth Failures | N/A — no auth yet |
| A08 Integrity Failures | N/A |
| A09 Logging/Monitoring Failures | Only `console.log` on startup; add request + error logging (e.g. `pino`, `morgan`) before prod |
| A10 SSRF | N/A — no outbound requests |

